# Testimonials Module Guide

## Public Endpoints
### List Testimonials
- `GET /api/testimonials`
- Query Parameters:
  - `limit`: Number of testimonials to return
  - `random`: Return random testimonials (boolean)

## Admin Endpoints
### Manage Testimonials
- List all: `GET /api/admin/testimonials`
- Create: `POST /api/admin/testimonials`
- Update: `PUT/PATCH /api/admin/testimonials/{testimonial_id}`
- Delete: `DELETE /api/admin/testimonials/{testimonial_id}`

### Testimonial Fields
- `author_name`: Name of the testimonial author
- `author_title_company`: Author's title and company
- `author_avatar_url`: URL to author's avatar image
- `body`: The testimonial content
- `rating`: Rating (1-5)
- `source`: Source of the testimonial
- `is_published`: Publication status
- `published_at`: Publication date

